---
import {
   ArrowRight,
   BarChart3,
   Bot,
   CircleCheck,
   FileText,
   MessageSquareText,
   Upload,
} from "@lucide/astro";
import { Reveal } from "../components/reveal";
---

<section
   class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-background py-4"
   aria-label="Operação recorrente"
>
   <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-7xl flex-col gap-4 px-2 sm:px-4">
      <Reveal client:visible>
         <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-muted-foreground">
               Operação nativa para recorrência
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-3xl leading-tight font-black text-foreground text-balance sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">
               Do contrato ao caixa, com o contexto do cliente no meio
            </h2>
            <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-base">
               Montte combina billing, uso medido e financeiro em fluxos de trabalho que
               mostram o que aconteceu, o que precisa de cobrança e qual ação vem depois.
            </p>
         </div>
      </Reveal>

      <div class="grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-6">
         <Reveal className="lg:col-span-4" client:visible>
            <article class="flex h-full min-h-[330px] flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-secondary/30 p-4">
               <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Escolha o fluxo operacional</h3>
                  <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                     Comece por uma rotina concreta: cobrar uso, revisar inadimplência,
                     conciliar receita ou entender a saúde de um cliente.
                  </p>
               </div>

               <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-3xl flex-col gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-card p-4 shadow-2xl shadow-background/60">
                  <div class="grid gap-2 md:grid-cols-3">
                     <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border border-primary/60 bg-primary/10 p-4">
                        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-2 rounded-md bg-primary/15 text-primary">
                           <Bot class="size-4" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                           <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Billing Agent</p>
                           <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                              Gera cobrança a partir de contrato, uso e estado do cliente.
                           </p>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-background/70 p-4">
                        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-2 rounded-md bg-secondary text-muted-foreground">
                           <FileText class="size-4" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                           <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Finance Agent</p>
                           <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                              Reconcilia receita, pendências e Centros de Custo.
                           </p>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-background/70 p-4">
                        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-2 rounded-md bg-secondary text-muted-foreground">
                           <CircleCheck class="size-4" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                           <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Customer State</p>
                           <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                              Mostra assinatura, uso, fatura e próxima ação.
                           </p>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-background/80 p-2">
                     <span class="flex-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground">Pergunte sobre uso, cobrança ou caixa...</span>
                     <span class="rounded-full border border-border/70 px-2 py-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                        Billing Agent
                     </span>
                     <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-2 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground">
                        <ArrowRight class="size-4" />
                     </span>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </article>
         </Reveal>

         <Reveal className="lg:col-span-2" delay={0.1} client:visible>
            <article class="flex h-full min-h-[330px] flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-secondary/30 p-4">
               <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Pergunte sobre a operação</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                     Respostas com base no estado real do cliente, não em texto solto.
                  </p>
               </div>

               <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-card p-4 shadow-xl shadow-background/50">
                  <div class="rounded-lg bg-primary/10 p-4 text-xs font-medium text-foreground">
                     Quais clientes passaram da cota este mês?
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                     <MessageSquareText class="size-4 text-primary" />
                     Revisando uso, faturas e contratos...
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-background/80 p-2">
                     <span class="flex-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground">Ask anything...</span>
                     <span class="rounded-full border border-border/70 px-2 py-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                        Customer State
                     </span>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </article>
         </Reveal>

         <Reveal className="lg:col-span-2" delay={0.2} client:visible>
            <article class="flex h-full min-h-[300px] flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-secondary/30 p-4">
               <div class="rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-card p-4 shadow-xl shadow-background/50">
                  <div class="grid grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr_0.6fr] gap-2 border-b border-border/60 pb-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                     <span>Cliente</span>
                     <span>Status</span>
                     <span>Risco</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="grid gap-2 pt-2 text-xs text-foreground">
                     <div class="grid grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr_0.6fr] gap-2">
                        <span>Acme</span>
                        <span>Uso acima</span>
                        <span class="text-chart-3">Médio</span>
                     </div>
                     <div class="grid grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr_0.6fr] gap-2">
                        <span>Northwind</span>
                        <span>Fatura aberta</span>
                        <span class="text-primary">Baixo</span>
                     </div>
                     <div class="grid grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr_0.6fr] gap-2">
                        <span>Stark</span>
                        <span>Pagamento falhou</span>
                        <span class="text-destructive">Alto</span>
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>

               <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Veja o quadro completo</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                     Clientes, contratos, uso, cobrança e caixa no mesmo recorte operacional.
                  </p>
               </div>
            </article>
         </Reveal>

         <Reveal className="lg:col-span-4" delay={0.3} client:visible>
            <article class="flex h-full min-h-[300px] flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-secondary/30 p-4">
               <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-md flex-col gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-card p-4 shadow-2xl shadow-background/60">
                  <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-2">
                     <span class="block rounded-lg p-4 bg-secondary"></span>
                     <span class="block rounded-lg p-4 bg-primary/30"></span>
                     <span class="flex items-center justify-center p-4 rounded-lg bg-primary/15 text-primary">
                        <BarChart3 class="size-4" />
                     </span>
                     <span class="block rounded-lg p-4 bg-secondary"></span>
                     <span class="block rounded-lg p-4 bg-secondary"></span>
                  </div>
                  <button class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-background/80 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground">
                     <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <Upload class="size-4 text-primary" />
                        Contract upload
                     </span>
                     <CircleCheck class="size-4 text-primary" />
                  </button>
                  <button class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-primary/15 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-primary">
                     <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <BarChart3 class="size-4" />
                        Gerar análise de cobrança
                     </span>
                     <ArrowRight class="size-4" />
                  </button>
               </div>

               <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Transforme contrato em cobrança</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                     Leia regras comerciais, compare com uso real e gere a ação financeira certa.
                  </p>
               </div>
            </article>
         </Reveal>

         <Reveal className="lg:col-span-3" delay={0.4} client:visible>
            <article class="flex h-full min-h-[300px] flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-secondary/30 p-4">
               <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-sm rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-card p-4 shadow-xl shadow-background/50">
                  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                     <p class="font-semibold text-foreground">Análise Acme · maio</p>
                     <p><strong class="text-foreground">Uso:</strong> 18.420 eventos, 14% acima da cota.</p>
                     <p><strong class="text-foreground">Contrato:</strong> cobrança incremental aplicável.</p>
                     <p><strong class="text-foreground">Financeiro:</strong> reconhecer R$ 1.284,00 em receita.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>

               <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Analise exceções em segundos</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                     Saia do relatório estático para uma leitura clara de contrato, uso e ação.
                  </p>
               </div>
            </article>
         </Reveal>

         <Reveal className="lg:col-span-3" delay={0.5} client:visible>
            <article class="flex h-full min-h-[300px] flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border/70 bg-secondary/30 p-4 text-center">
               <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-4 rounded-full border border-primary/30 bg-primary/15 text-primary shadow-2xl shadow-primary/20">
                  <Bot class="size-4" />
               </div>
               <div class="flex max-w-md flex-col items-center gap-2">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Vá mais fundo quando precisar</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                     Do resumo executivo ao dado de origem, avance sem perder contexto.
                  </p>
               </div>
               <a
                  href="#waitlist"
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-border/70 bg-background/80 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-foreground"
               >
                  Explorar Montte AI
                  <ArrowRight class="size-4" />
               </a>
            </article>
         </Reveal>
      </div>
   </div>
</section>
